<h2 class="bold font-l">48$</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After having a hit on him for most of the episode, the ending reveals that the amount of money Krusty owed the mob...was simply 48$. He gives the Don a fifty and even gets $2 in change. </p>
